---
<form action="#" method="POST" class="registration-form" netlify {/* This name is important for Netlify UI */}
                    data-netlify="true"
                    netlify-honeypot="bot-field" > 
                    <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contact" />

                    {/* Honeypot field for spam prevention. Should be hidden for users. */}
                     <p class="hidden" style="display: none;">
                         <label>Don’t fill this out if you’re human: <input name="bot-field"></label>
                     </p>

                    <p class="form-intro">
    Compila il modulo sottostante per richiedere l'iscrizione. Verrai ricontattato via email per la conferma e i dettagli di fatturazione.
  </p>
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="nome">Nome</label>
    <input type="text" id="nome" name="nome" required>
  </div>
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="cognome">Cognome</label>
    <input type="text" id="cognome" name="cognome" required>
  </div>
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="email">Email</label>
    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
  </div>
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="telefono">Telefono</label>
    <input type="tel" id="telefono" name="telefono" required>
  </div>
  <div class="form-group">
    
    <div class="radio-group">
        <input type="radio" id="piano" name="plan" class="radio-input" required>
        <label for="piano" class="radio-label">
            <span class="title">Piano Base</span>
            <span class="description">Perfect for beginners</span>
            <div class="checkmark">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.2L4.8 12l-1.4 1.4L9 19 21 7l-1.4-1.4L9 16.2z"/></svg>
            </div>
        </label>

        <input type="radio" id="standard" name="plan" class="radio-input" required>
        <label for="standard" class="radio-label">
            <span class="title">Standard</span>
            <span class="description">Most popular choice</span>
            <div class="checkmark">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.2L4.8 12l-1.4 1.4L9 19 21 7l-1.4-1.4L9 16.2z"/></svg>
            </div>
        </label>

        <input type="radio" id="premium" name="plan" class="radio-input" required>
        <label for="premium" class="radio-label">
            <span class="title">Premium</span>
            <span class="description">Advanced features included</span>
            <div class="checkmark">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.2L4.8 12l-1.4 1.4L9 19 21 7l-1.4-1.4L9 16.2z"/></svg>
            </div>
        </label>
    </div>


   
  </div>
   <div class="form-group privacy-consent">
        <input type="checkbox" id="privacy" name="privacy" value="accepted" required>
        <label for="privacy">
            Ho letto e accetto l'<a href="/privacy" target="_blank">Informativa sulla Privacy</a> e i <a href="/termini" target="_blank">Termini del Servizio</a>.
        </label>
   </div>
  <button type="submit">Invia Richiesta</button>
   <p class="form-note">
       Nota: L'attivazione del servizio e la fatturazione verranno gestite manualmente via email dopo la verifica della richiesta.
   </p>
</form>

<style>
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter  :wght@400;600&display=swap');

   .registration-form {
     max-width: 600px;
     margin: 0 auto;
     padding: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 2);
     border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
     border-radius: 8px;
     background-color: var(--light-gray);
   }
   .form-intro, .form-note {
     margin-bottom: var(--spacing-unit);
     font-size: 0.95rem;
     color: var(--secondary-color);
   }
    .form-note {
      margin-top: var(--spacing-unit);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
    .privacy-consent {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start; /* Align checkbox with start of label */
        gap: 0.5rem; /* Space between checkbox and label */
        margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 1.5);
    }
    .privacy-consent input[type="checkbox"] {
       margin-top: 0.2em; /* Align checkbox better with text */
       flex-shrink: 0; /* Prevent checkbox shrinking */
    }
    .privacy-consent label {
       font-weight: normal; /* Make privacy label normal weight */
       margin-bottom: 0; /* Remove default label margin */
       font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    .privacy-consent label a {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }
    button[type="submit"] {
        width: 100%;
        padding: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 0.8) 0;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .radio-group {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            background: white;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 800px;
        }

        .radio-input {
            position: absolute;
            opacity: 0;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .radio-label {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.64, 0.09, 0.08, 1);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .radio-label::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a90e2, #6a11cb);
            border-radius: inherit;
            transform: scale(0);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .radio-label:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(74, 144, 226, 0.2);
        }

        .radio-input:checked + .radio-label {
            color: white;
        }

        .radio-input:checked + .radio-label::before {
            transform: scale(1);
        }

        .radio-input:checked + .radio-label .checkmark {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: scale(1);
        }

        .radio-label .title {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .radio-label .description {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: #666;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .checkmark {
            position: absolute;
            right: 1rem;
            top: 1rem;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: scale(0.7);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .checkmark svg {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            fill: white;
        }

        /* Bounce animation */
        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-5px); }
        }

        .radio-input:checked + .radio-label {
            animation: bounce 0.3s ease;
        }


</style>